== 评价 ==

部分西方评论对合辑修改原版游戏表示不满。例如克雷格·哈里斯批评称，《[[铁板阵|铁板阵]]》的自动开火设定破坏了原版的难度<ref>Harris, Craig.  [http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/500/500563p1.html IGN: Xevious (Classic NES Series) Review] {{Wayback|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/500/500563p1.html |date=20120205061336 }}.  June 4, 2004.</ref>。《[[超级马里奥兄弟|超级马里奥兄弟]]》屏幕比例变化让图形变得古怪<ref name="smb">Gerstmann, Jeff.  [http://gamespot.com/gba/action/famicomminisupermariobros/review.html GameSpot: Super Mario Bros. review] {{Wayback|url=http://gamespot.com/gba/action/famicomminisupermariobros/review.html |date=20071030111000 }}.  [[GameSpot|GameSpot]].  June 8, 2004</ref><ref>Harris, Craig. [http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/499/499470p1.html "Super Mario Bros." review] {{Wayback|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/499/499470p1.html |date=20090716183941 }}.  IGN.  June 4, 2004.</ref>。

评论对游戏定价表示批评。许多评论称一款游戏20美元价格过高。GameSpot和IGn都提到，任天堂在《[[塞尔达传说合辑|塞尔达传说合辑]]》中免费赠送了《[[塞尔达传说_(游戏)|塞尔达传说]]》和《[[林克的冒险|林克的冒险]]》，但他们也指出该游戏可以携带<ref name="gszelda">Gerstmann, Jeff.  [http://gamespot.com/gba/rpg/famicomminithelegendofzelda/review.html "Classic NES Series: The Legend of Zelda for Game Boy Advance Review"] {{Wayback|url=http://gamespot.com/gba/rpg/famicomminithelegendofzelda/review.html |date=20071014055230 }}.  GameSpot.  June 8, 2004.</ref><ref name="ignzelda">Harris, Craig. [http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/499/499860p1.html "IGN: The Legend of Zelda (Classic NES Series) Review] {{Wayback|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/499/499860p1.html |date=20120806201437 }}.  IGN.  June 4, 2004.</ref>。但是评论一直认为，值得为《超级马里奥兄弟》、《塞尔达传说》、《恶魔城》、《林克的冒险》和《马里奥医生》等游戏购买卡带。

